98\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dodanli won gold in the all-around at the Turkish Artistic Gymnastics Championship earlier this summer.\\u00c2  Dodanli was the first Sooner to compete in Paris, with men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gymnastics qualification on Saturday.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1767, \"end\": 1772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999310162149, \"rank\": 6.898384377948283e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The individual all-around final will be Wednesday.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Event finals start Saturday.\\u00c2  Fraschilla will represent OU in a different way as an assistant coach on the USA Men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 3x3 Basketball National Team.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 2025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oklahoma\", \"score\": 0.9506045905469258, \"rank\": 0.05196209858906158, \"text\": \"OU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oklahoma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oklahoma\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He walked onto the Sooners\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 basketball team before graduating in 2015 and following in his father\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s footsteps as a coach.\\u00c2  This is only the second Olympics with 3x3 basketball, however, the U.S. did not qualify for the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s first men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 3x3 game in an Olympics will be against Serbia at 3:35 p.m. Tuesday.\\u00c2  