pedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was a McDonald\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s All-American before getting to OU in 2006.\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2956, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She averaged 10.6 points a game as a senior in 2009-10 before a brief WNBA career.\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 3039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She then got into coaching, currently serving as an assistant for the Connecticut Sun.\\u00c2  Nigeria plays France at 10:15 a.m. Thursday after beating Australia 75-62 early Monday morning.\\u00c2  Born in London, Pipi will compete in a pair of events for Great Britain, including the 400 meter and 4x400 relay, in her second Olympics at 28.\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3110, \"end\": 3121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies\", \"score\": 0.6769077481010023, \"rank\": 0.4467248386228806, \"text\": \"Connecticut\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UConn_Huskies\"}, {\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9892554706192859, \"rank\": 0.007838190814057679, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3143, \"end\": 3149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9928546783117193, \"rank\": 0.0038059181263958883, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3187, \"end\": 3196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia